# Hi.

I will watch Rick and Morty in Pupin and drink beer and everyone is welcome to join.

If you want to drink beers, please text me or facebook message me on the [facebook page](http://www.facebook.com/rick-morty-pupin). I will make sure to get enough beers for everybody.

This page exists because facebook wants u 2 have a website b4 u make a facebook group (i guess).
